### Bugs
* `Client.readEntry` does not return exact length
* `zig build test` does not run all test.zig tests
* repl `ls` command is leaking memory

### Features
* client better line editor
* client read file
* client download file
* ls coloring (distincting dirs from files)
* server should handle multiple clients
* server should provide max length of paths
* upload file
* remove file
* directory manipulation
* client history
* parallel transfers
* multi-root
* proxy
* authentication
* per-dir/file permissions
* compression
* encryption

